  "merger_description": "Autodesk, Inc. (**Autodesk**) proposes to acquire 100% of the share capital in MaintainX, Inc. (**MaintainX**).\n\nAutodesk is a software company which supplies software products in the architecture, engineering, construction, manufacturing, media, and entertainment industries. Autodesk\u2019s core products include Revit, Fusion and AutoCAD, which allow for computer-aided design, drafting and management.\n\nMaintainX is a software company which supplies a computerised maintenance management system that assists companies to manage the day-to-day work of maintaining physical assets. MaintainX\u2019s platform includes enterprise asset management software, which enables the management, tracking and organisation of assets across their entire lifecycle.",
